args.canonical_rel_desc: Indicates that an ethical issue, dilemma, or concept is about or related to a particular system, domain, or context.
args.justification: The relation expresses a general aboutness/scope link between an ethical dilemma and its domain (AI systems). Using a more generic predicate-style name 'pertains_to' improves reusability across the KG and better matches standard aboutness semantics than the verb-form label 'concerns', while keeping the same class and group.
